Class ConcurrentHashSet<E>

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.jppf.utils.collections.ConcurrentHashSet<E>
  • Type Parameters:
    E - the type of objects in the set.
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    Iterable<E>, Collection<E>, Set<E>

    public class ConcurrentHashSet<E>
extends Object
implements Set<E>
    A concurrent et implementation backed by a ConcurrentHashMap.
